Output docs/demos/demo-congestion.gif

Set Shell zsh
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 1100
Set Height 650
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 15

Type "# Data Space Grid — 1000-Household Congestion Management Demo"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type ".venv/bin/python3.14 examples/congestion_management_demo.py"
Enter
Sleep 12s

Sleep 3s
